Pythagora is a VS Code extension that helps developers create apps by interacting with them using AI. Powered by GPT-4 and GPT Pilot, it can write production-ready, modular code, debug errors, and fix its own code. It guides users through the app development process by asking clarifying questions when needed and can handle tasks such as architecture design, feature implementation, and deployment. Pythagora aims to simplify coding, making it accessible for junior developers to quickly advance their skills【6†source】. For more details, visit [Pythagora's website](https://www.pythagora.ai).
